findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions withdrawTokens() and withdrawFees() use loops to remove depositId from withdrawal addresses and tokens mapping, and to withdraw fee from token fee addresses list, respectively. If there are long lists, the function will be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to modify critical parameters without being renounced.
